section.section:
Of the 10 members:
One shall be a licensed physician who specializes in radiology;
One shall be a licensed physician who specializes in radiology and who supervises a radiologist assistant;
One shall be a licensed physician who specializes in nuclear medicine;
One shall be a licensed physician who specializes in radiation oncology;
One shall be a radiation therapist;
One shall be a radiographer;
One shall be a radiologist assistant;
One shall be a nuclear medicine technologist;
One shall be a consumer member; and
One shall be a member of the Board.
